  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Mining Ships are mobile resource extraction ships. They
  mine resources that are in high demand, returning them to your nearest sp=
ace
  port.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Mining ships work for your empire, but they are not you=
rs.
  They belong to the private citizens in your empire.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Thus you cannot assign missions to Mining ships</span>.=
